<br>
Fearless: i used this when i was dueling a necro and in a few other situations it was great<br>
<br>
Evasive: i dont use this<br>
<br>
Charge: rarely... if im soloing green mobs for faction or whatever i would use this because it adds good dmg and it refreshes pretty fast<br>
<br>
Mighty strike: i use this when im frenzy and we need to kill the mob faster<br>
<br>
Defensive: when im main tank on raid (even when im not sometimes), when too many mobs are hitting me in a group, and after a bad pull. i use defensive a LOT even after nerf.<br>
<br>
Furious: ive used this a few times, but the best was in loio when i was camping the sarnak earring of station. i remember i had 20 or so sarnaks hitting me and when i hit furious (even though my health was full) they all took a good deal of damage, i was invul for a bit, and my hit spam was INSANE. this disc is a lot like enrage its great. im sure its even more impressive when you have a large number of mobs on you that hit fast. <p><p align="left"><b>-garyen varillious al'dar<br>
